# Swarm gateway endpoints. The public gateways accept uploads with wildcard CORS
# and serve reads — no proxy or wallet signature needed.
#
# Upload endpoint: api.gateway.ethswarm.org accepts POSTs against any batch ID
# it knows. A batch you bought via beeport.ethswarm.org will work here because
# both share the same underlying Bee node (godfather2.ethswarm.org).
VITE_SWARM_UPLOAD_URL=https://api.gateway.ethswarm.org

# Read endpoint: download.gateway.ethswarm.org serves HTML pages directly.
# api.gateway redirects HTML to a "forbidden" page for phishing protection,
# so we use download for resolving uploaded sites.
VITE_SWARM_READ_URL=https://download.gateway.ethswarm.org

# WalletConnect Cloud project id — public-by-design
# Get one at https://cloud.walletconnect.com
VITE_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=

# Alchemy API key — one key works for both mainnet (ENS resolution) and
# Gnosis Chain (postage stamp registry reads). Get one at
# https://dashboard.alchemy.com (free tier is plenty).
# Note: Vite bakes this into the client bundle, so the key is public.
# Lock it down via Alchemy's Allowed Origins (Apps → Networks).
# If empty, falls through to public RPCs (LlamaRPC, Blast, gnosischain.com, gateway.fm).
VITE_ALCHEMY_API_KEY=
